title: MAVERICK 106 Stage West [retr?tv]
description:
MAVERICK 1x06 Stage West     27 Oct 1957

The Fallons have bushwacked 2 prospectors to try to find out where their silver mine is located, but trigger-happy Wes Fallon (Edd &#039;Kookie" Byrnes) shoots Sam Harris before he can reveal its location. His partner reveals that the only person who knows is Mrs. Harris who is coming in from the East with a map. The Fallons ride off to the stage stop little knowing that Bret Maverick will come upon the dying Harris and learn from him that the mine is on hostile Indian land.

Stars James Garner as Bret Maverick 
Guest Stars:  >> Eddy "Kookie" Byrnes!!! (Wes Fallon :),Chubby Johnson (Simmons), Ray Teal (Mart Fallon), Jim Bannon (Matson), Fern Barry (Ella Taylor), Peter Brown (Rip Fallon), Michael Dante (Sam Harris), Howard Negley (Sheriff Tibbs), Erin O&#039;Brien (Linda Harris), Buddy Shaw (Dave Taylor), Ollie O&#039;Toole (McLean)
First aired: 27 October 1957

MPEG1/320x240/50min

*REPOST* of the file I originally posted on demonoid on 27 Oct 2007 in celebration of Maverick&#039;s 50th birthday. How appropriate that Kookie should attend! :)
